N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 21 ยง 5019.6 - Subject matter list

State Regulations

The records access officer shall maintain a reasonably
detailed current list, by subject matter, of all records in the system's
possession, regardless of whether such records are available pursuant to the

Freedom of Information Law or the Personal Privacy Protection Law. Such list
shall be posted on the system's website (www.nystrs.org). Notes
